{"tid":1240612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立會擬押後21號審議明日大嶼研究","createTime":"2019-06-18T11:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T13:01:33.000Z","uid":13754,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"336b528d2ae24b4e5a9e2482d512b4d2ce6d5ea7","tid":1240612,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:41:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2378498/立法會擬押後審議明日大嶼研究\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2378498%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%93%AC%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BC%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=c6de4129\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2378498/立法會擬押後審議明日大嶼研究</a><br />\n<br />\n「明日大嶼」中部水域人工島研究撥款，原定在本周五(6月21日)，提交到立法會財委會審議，為避開近期政治風波，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府將撥款調至議程最後一項，意味有機會立法會暑假休會前難以通過。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n立法會工務小組上月25日(周六)在20 票贊成、16 票反對下，通過「明日大嶼」中部水域人工島5.5 億元的研究撥款申請，並提交財委會審議，按照財委會近期議程，原本將於周五審議，並屬於首項議題。<br />\n<br />\n不過，由於近期社會政治氣氛高漲，為免有爭議的明日大嶼方案會再引起更多紛爭，政府將撥款議程調動，並將中部水域人工島研究撥款調至周五議程的第21項，亦即是最後一項。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據估計，若果政府之後不再改動議程，撥款議案有機會沒法趕及今個立法會期內通過，須在暑假過後、立法會復會後才能夠作審議。"},{"pid":"d7498baacad70ba54ca8d9c4d4cb4830eb802ebd","tid":1240612,"uid":13754,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:43:43.000Z","msg":"21號似乎冇合理而夠大嘅目標，20號未必適合成為死線，我希望各位同路要諗諗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f4440b08bad37c29c3a0f4eb065b2e75a21bce","tid":1240612,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:44:51.000Z","msg":"唔好縮呀你 唔係好打得西口西面既咩"},{"pid":"c61415cdae2d5f379affffbe6c52696215f9a3e4","tid":1240612,"uid":15564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:45:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">擬</span></span>"},{"pid":"08dfff0c25124adfc870e3180b81ae45155285eb","tid":1240612,"uid":10089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"擬你老母"},{"pid":"4d439f19b103d78fc2181bba8809e765a3a41ac2","tid":1240612,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ac827f734d20013daf3261fa6006f6550df29a","tid":1240612,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c61415cdae2d5f379affffbe6c52696215f9a3e4","tid":1240612,"uid":15564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:45:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">擬</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:50:47.000Z","msg":"放咗去最尾，即係好大可能傾唔切，要落下次"},{"pid":"fd5b381ec91097fb77902485080228ccf5fe3992","tid":1240612,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08dfff0c25124adfc870e3180b81ae45155285eb","tid":1240612,"uid":10089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"擬你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"我睇晒成篇文，政府放個item落最尾唔係擬<br />\n<br />\n要諗定嗰日真係咁嘅話係咪最適合行動，有冇alternative"},{"pid":"4fb87fb9a8b8e994e35110afbab94a8a60a84cad","tid":1240612,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:59:32.000Z","msg":"補返議程正本<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/fc/fc/agenda/fc20190621.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Ffc%2Fagenda%2Ffc20190621.htm&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=fedb7509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/fc/fc/agenda/fc20190621.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n明日大嶼，即係中部水域研究放咗去最尾，有機會傾唔切，大家留意返"},{"pid":"4ad2b5f33eff706175077f60d6b1eb3f4f6ec41b","tid":1240